reviews.review_text:
Another Rodaside Attraction.... Sick source.  Both sets flow like hot magma down the mountain and then slides into the steaming Pacific.............

Of note:  Jerry just goes to the moon on Big Railroad Blues.  No version like it.   I always wind up laughing listening to this BRB version, no matter how many times, because it is so over-the-top.
